data.description: Looking for some more space?! This is it! 4 bedroom, 2 bathroom home with a large 2 car garage sitting on almost a half an acre. This spacious home has updated flooring, bathroom vanities, windows, and a new roof! The kitchen is a great size for cooking, entertaining, and hosting all of those holiday gatherings! Almost every room has built in shelves, large closets and space for all of your storage needs. You can't beat this location, down the street from the brand new premier Kids Space Park, but also on a quiet street easily accessible to everything in town. Don't miss out on this beautiful home!
